{
  "texts": [
    "In the developed AH-CNN-LSTM model, essential features are extracted using the CNN technique, and the LSTM procedure is used to classify human motion intentions accurately.",
    "The main objective of the developed AH-CNN-LSTM-based human motion intention prediction model is to maximize the MCC (Matthews correlation coefficient) and reduce the FDR (false discovery rate), which is formulated in Eq.",
    "(18).F t1 = arg min {Hu cnn m,Ep cnn z,Hu Lstm c,Ep Lstm b } ( 1 Sq + Rd (18) The term Sq specifics the MCC and Rd illustrates the FDR.",
    "The hidden neuron count in CNN is presented as Hu cnn m and LSTM is specified as Hu Lstm c that is chosen in the limit [5,255].",
    "The count of epoch in LSTM is offered as Ep Lstm b, and CNN is signified as Ep cnn z, which is chosen in the bound of [5,50]."
  ]
}